{"word":"ὑποτοπέω","slug":"ὑποτοπέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὑποτοπέω</b></el> <el>(aor1 <el>-ετόπησα</el>) (aor1 <el>ὑπετοπήθην</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to suspect, surmise</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>; <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> et <a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <a href='S:person, personal'>pers.</a> <i>to suspect</i> him, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>so as <a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <el>ὑποτοπέομαι</el> <i>to suspect</i> a thing, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>; <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> et <a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a> <i>to suspect that . .</i> , <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}